Use Case 1 = Error Detection Agent
UPG would like to leverage an AI Agent to:
View the Azure SQL DB log database for Exceptions and Errors
Create a ticket in Azure DevOps corresponding to these Exceptions and Errors.
Highlight which errors are occurring more than once.
Fork a repo from the current main branch
Propose a fix for this exception/error using an LLM
Alert a human to view the changes/updates proposed.
Assist the human-in-loop to merge the branch back to main once the human-in-the-loop approves i
